OOC( I won't be able to post again untill Monday Morning.  Have a 
good weekend all.)



::Feline::
She smiled,"Good.  As soon as CyberShark is ready, we will go down 
there and get then.  I want you to hold a gun to my head and tell 
them that you will shoot me unless they let them go.  Then we all 
leave and go to the Allience base.

::Battera::
She decided that she had more of an advantage in the air than on the 
ground.  She opened ehr link to Zardus,"I have to return to the base 
for repairs.  I shall rejoin you shortly."  She Transformed into bat 
mode and flew off towards the alliance base.  She flew as hard as she 
could.  By the time she got to the base, her wing was torn and so 
badly damages that she her wing was almost shredded.  She walked 
inside and went to the CR room and stepped into a chamber to heal.

KitKat::
She looked at Drillbit.  "I am tired and would like to sleep for a 
bit. Please wake me when the others arrive."
She walked back into the CR chamber and fell asleep inside the 
chamber.

::Spears::
She was placed inside the chamber and cried in pain as she slowly 
healed.

GoldenEye::
She nodded to Dollen, "Yes, let's rejoin the others."

Shadow Wing::
She prayed to the matrix that she would live long enough to see 
Lunarpine again.

Squizzy::
Still inside the Allience CR chamber as Dark One left her.
